videos.description: Florida QB Feleipe Franks gets picked off on the 2-yard line by Vanderbilt's Joejuan Williams on the Gators' first possession.
videos.headline: Franks throws red zone INT

videos.description: Vanderbilt's Kyle Shurmur leads a 98-yard drive and finds Jared Pinkney in the end zone for a short touchdown to give the Commodores an early lead over the Gators.
videos.headline: Vandy strikes first on Shurmur TD pass

videos.description: Vanderbilt's Ke'Shawn Vaughn bounces to the outside and sprints up the sideline for a 43-yard gain, setting up a Commodores touchdown later in the drive.
videos.headline: Vandy RB Vaughn races for 43-yard gain

videos.description: Vanderbilt's Kyle Shurmur swings a pass to Ke'Shawn Vaughn, who races through the Florida defense and dives for the end zone on a 75-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Shurmur's pass to Vaughn goes 75 yards for Vanderbilt TD) 2018/10/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shurmur's pass to Vaughn goes 75 yards for Vandy TD

videos.description: Florida QB Feleipe Franks fumbles and Vanderbilt cannot scoop it up until Dayo Odeyingbo recovers over 30 yards downfield before it goes out of bounds.
videos.headline: Vandy kicks around Franks fumble for over 30 yards, finally recovers

videos.description: Jamauri Wakefield powers into the end zone from 7 yards out to extend Vanderbilt's lead over Florida.
videos.headline: Wakefield's TD extends Vandy lead

videos.description: Lamical Perine reaches the ball over the goal line and is initially ruled down, but a review overturns the play to a 7-yard Florida touchdown.
videos.headline: Perine reaches over goal line for 1st Florida TD

videos.description: Florida's James Houston IV is ejected for a targeting penalty on a punt return that gets both sidelines and head coaches fired up.
videos.headline: Tempers flare after Florida targeting penalty, ejection

videos.description: Feleipe Franks dumps a pass off to Lamical  Perine and he cuts through the Vanderbilt defense for a 63-yard gain, setting up a field goal before the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Perine's 63-yard catch sets up Gators field goal

videos.description: Vanderbilt running back Ke'Shawn Vaughn exits in the second quarter after racking up 131 total yards against Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vanderbilt's Vaughn leaves game in 2nd quarter) 2018/10/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Vaughn leaves game in 2nd quarter

videos.description: Florida punter Tommy Townsend runs a fake punt 18 yards up the middle, leading to a touchdown later in the possession.
videos.headline: Florida punter takes fake 18 yards

videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks throws a slant to Van Jefferson and he outraces Vanderbilt defenders for a 38-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Franks connects with Jefferson for 38-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Scarlett sheds a tackle and races for a 48-yard touchdown run to give Florida the lead over Vanderbilt for the first time.
videos.headline: Scarlett breaks free for 48-yard Florida TD

videos.description: Florida's Dameon Pierce coughs up the ball and Vanderbilt's Zaire Jones jumps on it, leading to a Vanderbilt field goal.
videos.headline: Vandy strips Florida RB, recovers fumble

videos.description: Feleipe Franks swings a pass out to Freddie Swain, who leaps over a Vanderbilt defender and lands in the end zone for an 11-yard Florida touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida WR Swain goes airborne for TD

videos.description: Dan Mullen and Derek Mason both have high praise for each other after they got into a heated exchange during Saturday's Florida-Vanderbilt game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Mason, Mullen speak after heated exchange) 2018/10/13

videos.headline: Mason, Mullen speak after heated exchange
